white_resampled = resample(white, replace = True, n_samples = len(black), random_state = 42)
ai_an_resampled = resample(ai_an, replace = True, n_samples = len(black), random_state = 42)

hispanic_resampled = resample(hispanic, replace = True, n_samples = len(black), random_state = 42)

In [270]:
fd_resampled.rename(columns = {'Sex':'Female'}, inplace = True)
fd_resampled['HeartDisease'] = fd_resampled['HeartDisease'].replace({'Yes': 1, 'No': 0})
fd_resampled["Female"] = fd_resampled["Female"].map({'Female' : 1, 'Male' : 0})
fd_resampled['Smoking'] = fd_resampled['Smoking'].map({'Yes' : 1, 'No' : 0})
fd_resampled['AlcoholDrinking'] = fd_resampled['AlcoholDrinking'].map({'Yes' : 1, 'No' : 0})
fd_resampled['Stroke'] = fd_resampled['Stroke'].map({'Yes' : 1, 'No' : 0})
fd_resampled['DiffWalking'] = fd_resampled['DiffWalking'].map({'Yes' : 1, 'No' : 0})
fd_resampled['PhysicalActivity'] = fd_resampled['PhysicalActivity'].map({'Yes' : 1, 'No' : 0})
fd_resampled['Asthma'] = fd_resampled['Asthma'].map({'Yes' : 1, 'No' : 0})
fd_resampled['KidneyDisease'] = fd_resampled['KidneyDisease'].map({'Yes' : 1, 'No' : 0})
fd_resampled['SkinCancer'] = fd_resampled['SkinCancer'].map({'Yes' : 1, 'No' : 0})
fd_resampled['Diabetic'] = fd_resampled['Diabetic'].map({'Yes' : 1, 'No' : 0})

Health = p.get_dummies(fd_resampled.GenHealth, prefix='Health')
Race = p.get_dummies(fd_resampled.Race, prefix='Race')

fd_resampled = fd_resampled.join(Health)
fd_resampled = fd_resampled.join(Race)

x = fd_resampled[['BMI', 'PhysicalHealth', 'MentalHealth', 'Diabetic', 'SleepTime']].fillna(0)
y = n.reshape(fd_resampled['HeartDisease'].values, (-1,1))

cat = ['Smoking', 'AlcoholDrinking', 'Stroke', 'DiffWalking', 'Female',
       'PhysicalActivity', 'Asthma', 'KidneyDisease', 'SkinCancer',
       'Health_Excellent', 'Health_Fair', 'Health_Good', 'Health_Poor',
       'Health_Very good', 'Race_American Indian/Alaskan Native', 'Race_Asian',
       'Race_Black', 'Race_Hispanic', 'Race_Other', 'Race_White']



del Health, Race

Function Creation for Training / Testing¶

In [271]:
def results(y_test, y_pred):
    confusion = metrics.confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred)

    TN = confusion[0, 0]
    FP = confusion[0, 1]
    FN = confusion[1, 0]
    TP = confusion[1, 1]
    
    print('-' * 50)
    print(f'Precision: {precision_score(y_test, y_pred, zero_division = 1)}')
    print(f'Recall: {recall_score(y_test, y_pred)}')
    print(f'F1: {f1_score(y_test, y_pred)}')
    print(f'False Positive Rate: {FP / (float(TN + FP))}')
    print(f'False Negative Rate: {FN / (float(TN + FP))}')
    print('-' * 50)
In [272]:
def curve(fit, X_test, y_test, alpha, model):
    fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(12,6))
    
    # ROC Curve
    plot_roc_curve(fit, X_test, y_test, name='original', ax=axes[0], alpha = alpha)
    axes[0].set_title(model + " ROC Curve")
    
    # Precision Recall Curve
    plot_precision_recall_curve(fit, X_test, y_test, name='original', ax=axes[1])
    axes[1].set_title(model + " Precision-Recall Curve")
    
    plt.show()
In [273]:
def fit_tests(x, fd, scaler, cat, stuff = True):
    zz = list(x.columns) + cat
    if stuff == True:
        scaler = scaler
        types = scaler.__class__.__name__
        
        model = scaler.fit(x)
        scaled_data = model.transform(x)
        df = n.column_stack((scaled_data, fd[cat].values))
        scaled = scaled_data
    
    else:
        types = 'Logistic Normalization'
        for j in x.columns: 
            x['norm ' + j] = (1+x[j])/2 # (-1,1] -> (0,1]
            x['lognorm '+ j] = n.log(x['norm ' + j])
        
        cols = [c for c in x.columns if c.lower()[:7] == 'lognorm ']
        x=x[cols]
        df = n.column_stack((x.values, fd[cat].values))
        scaled = x.values
    
    return df, scaled
In [274]:
def test(df, fd, Algo, types):
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df, n.reshape(fd['HeartDisease'].values, (-1,1)), test_size=0.2)
    logreg = Algo
    model = logreg.__class__.__name__
    fitted = logreg.fit(X_train, y_train)
    
    y_pred = logreg.predict(X_test)
    print(f'Metrics of Test Set with {types} with {model} Algorithm')
    results(y_test, n.reshape(y_pred, (-1,1)))
    curve(fitted, X_test, y_test, 0.6, types + ' ' + model)
In [275]:
def test_fea_sel(df, fd, Algo, types):
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df, n.reshape(fd['HeartDisease'].values, (-1,1)), test_size=0.2)
    selector = SelectFromModel(Algo).fit(X_train, y_train)
#     print(f'Estimator Coefficient: {selector.estimator_.coef_}')
#     print('-' * 100)
    print(f'Threshold: {selector.threshold_}')
    print('-' * 100)
    print(f'Get Support: {selector.get_support()}')
    print('-' * 100)
    print(f'X_train Transformed: {selector.transform(X_train)}')
    print('-' * 100)
In [276]:
def lr_test(df, fd, types, c = 0.05):
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df, n.reshape(fd['HeartDisease'].values, (-1,1)), test_size=0.2)
    logreg = LogisticRegression(C = c)
    model = logreg.__class__.__name__
    fitted = logreg.fit(X_train, y_train)
    
    y_pred = logreg.predict(X_test)
    print(f'Metrics of Test Set with {types} with {model} Algorithm')
    results(y_test, n.reshape(y_pred, (-1,1)))
    curve(fitted, X_test, y_test, 0.6, types + ' ' + model)
In [277]:
def lr_test_fea_sel(df, fd, types, c = 0.05):
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df, n.reshape(fd['HeartDisease'].values, (-1,1)), test_size=0.2)
    selector = SelectFromModel(LogisticRegression(C = c)).fit(X_train, y_train)
    print('Logistic Regression Model - Feature Selection')
    print('-' * 100)
    print(f'Estimator Coefficient: {selector.estimator_.coef_}')
    print('-' * 100)
    print(f'Threshold: {selector.threshold_}')
    print('-' * 100)
    print(f'Get Support: {selector.get_support()}')
    print('-' * 100)
    print(f'X_train Transformed: {selector.transform(X_train)}')
    print('-' * 100)
In [278]:
def rf_test(df, fd, types, n_est = 500, max_leaf_nodes = 5):
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df, n.reshape(fd['HeartDisease'].values, (-1,1)), test_size=0.2)
    logreg = RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators = n_est, max_leaf_nodes = max_leaf_nodes)
    model = logreg.__class__.__name__
    fitted = logreg.fit(X_train, y_train)
    
    y_pred = logreg.predict(X_test)
    print(f'Metrics of Test Set with {types} with {model} Algorithm')
    results(y_test, n.reshape(y_pred, (-1,1)))
    curve(fitted, X_test, y_test, 0.6, types + ' ' + model)
In [279]:
def rf_test_fea_sel(df, fd, types, n_est = 500, max_leaf_nodes = 5):
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df, n.reshape(fd['HeartDisease'].values, (-1,1)), test_size=0.2)
    selector = SelectFromModel(RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators = n_est, max_leaf_nodes = max_leaf_nodes)).fit(X_train, y_train)
    print('Random Forest Model - Feature Selection')
    print('-' * 100)
#     print(f'Estimator Coefficient: {selector.estimator_.coef_}')
#     print('-' * 100)
    print(f'Threshold: {selector.threshold_}')
    print('-' * 100)
    print(f'Get Support: {selector.get_support()}')
    print('-' * 100)
    print(f'X_train Transformed: {selector.transform(X_train)}')
    print('-' * 100)
In [280]:
def nb_test(df, fd, types, alpha = 0.5):
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df, n.reshape(fd['HeartDisease'].values, (-1,1)), test_size=0.2)
    logreg = BernoulliNB(alpha = alpha)
    model = logreg.__class__.__name__
    fitted = logreg.fit(X_train, y_train)
    
    y_pred = logreg.predict(X_test)
    print(f'Metrics of Test Set with {types} with {model} Algorithm')
    results(y_test, n.reshape(y_pred, (-1,1)))
    curve(fitted, X_test, y_test, 0.6, types + ' ' + model)
In [281]:
def nb_test_fea_sel(df, fd, types, alpha = 0.5):
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df, n.reshape(fd['HeartDisease'].values, (-1,1)), test_size=0.2)
    selector = SelectFromModel(BernoulliNB(alpha = alpha)).fit(X_train, y_train)
    print('Naive Bayes Model - Feature Selection')
    print('-' * 100)
#     print(f'Estimator Coefficient: {selector.estimator_.coef_}')
#     print('-' * 100)
    print(f'Threshold: {selector.threshold_}')
    print('-' * 100)
    print(f'Get Support: {selector.get_support()}')
    print('-' * 100)
    print(f'X_train Transformed: {selector.transform(X_train)}')
    print('-' * 100)

        print()
